        <updateDate>2007-06-07T16:25:15Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Fairness for Disabled Students Act of 2007 - Amends federal housing law to exempt from the prohibition against specified public housing rental assistance (&quot;Section 8 assistance&quot;) persons with disabilities who were not receiving such assistance as of November 30, 2005.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
