    <title>Fairness for Disabled Students Act of 2007</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To fully exempt persons with disabilities from the prohibition against providing section 8 rental assistance to college students.</title>
